---
import AppPageLayout from "../../layouts/AppPageLayout.astro";
import { Header } from "../../app/components/Header";
import { Footer } from "../../app/components/Footer";
---

<AppPageLayout
  title="Terms and Conditions | Pokedoku Helper and Pokedoku Details"
  description="Terms and conditions for using the Pokedoku Helper website and Pokedoku Details Devvit app."
  path="/terms-and-conditions/"
>
  <div class="app overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header
      title="Pokedoku Helper"
      subtitle="Legal information"
      currentPage="home"
      client:load
    />

    <main class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-8">
        <h1 class="m-0 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Terms and Conditions</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: May 7, 2026</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">By using Pokedoku Helper (website) or Pokedoku Details (Devvit app), you agree to these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use either service.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Use of the Service</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">Pokedoku Helper and Pokedoku Details provide informational tools and statistics related to Pokedoku. You may use these services for personal, non-commercial use and must not misuse, disrupt, or attempt unauthorized access.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">All original content and code in these services are owned by Pokedoku Helper / Pokedoku Details unless otherwise stated. Pokemon and Pokedoku-related trademarks and assets belong to their respective owners.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">No Warranty</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">These services are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee uninterrupted access, completeness, or accuracy of all content.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">To the fullest extent permitted by law, Pokedoku Helper / Pokedoku Details is not liable for any damages resulting from your use of or inability to use the website or Devvit app.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">We may update these terms from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised "Last updated" date.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Contact</h2>
        <p class="m-0 leading-7 text-slate-700">If you have questions about these terms, please open an issue at <a class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/jlast/pokedoku-solver/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/jlast/pokedoku-solver/issues</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer client:load />
  </div>
</AppPageLayout>
